LuaCSGO: A Lua API for CSGO game hacking

The main script must be placed at "steamapps\common\Counter-Strike Global Offensive\LuaCSGO\LuaCSGO.lua". Additional scripts can be used but they must be included (require("LuaCSGO/CustomScriptName")) by the main script.

Checkout the example script at <link>

